{
  "stem": "9723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There are not very many hotels, so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Uh, one of them was, uh very friendly, brought me a BB gun, which I was very fond of.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, uh, I guess those were pretty good years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she was not Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I guess she was either Polish or Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had, uh, I remember she had a number of Russian, uh, soldier boyfriends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes, they would come to visit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of them was a, uh, was a pilot in the Russian air force.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was hoping that maybe she could persuade him to take me for a flight in a, in a fighter plane, but [LAUGHS] never happened.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say so, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, uh, had no, uh, no particular problems or concerns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh, it was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, nobody really knew what was going to happen, how long the peace with, uh, with Russia and Germany would last, because the war was still going on in the west.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, but I wasn't concerned with these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, uh, I think it was June, 1941.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it looked like history repeated itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody knew anything was coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But all of a sudden, again, there were German planes overhead dropping bombs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was the first sign.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, uh, we went to the bomb shelter again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And didn't take very long for the Germans to, uh, to, uh, to, to come, because they didn't have very far to go.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Uh, so, uh, the first day after the war started, number of Russians started fleeing to Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Several of them stayed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember there were several Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know why they stayed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Um, one of my father's patients-- there are certain things that I do remember-- one of my father's patients was a Russian official.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
